     1Ôćĺ# color
     3ÔćĺColor lets you use colorized outputs in terms of [ANSI Escape
     4ÔćĺCodes](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ANSI_escape_code#Colors) in Go (Golang). It
     5Ôćĺhas support for Windows too! The API can be used in several ways, pick one that
     6Ôćĺsuits you.
     7Ôćĺ
     8Ôćĺ![Color](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/438920/96832689-03b3e000-13f4-11eb-9803-46f4c4de3406.jpg)
     9Ôćĺ
