   142Ôćĺ### Disable/Enable color
   144ÔćĺThere might be a case where you want to explicitly disable/enable color output. the 
   145Ôćĺ`go-isatty` package will automatically disable color output for non-tty output streams 
      ÔćĺÔÇŽ
   177Ôćĺ## GitHub Actions
   179ÔćĺTo output color in GitHub Actions (or other CI systems that support ANSI colors), make sure to set `color.NoColor = false` so that it bypasses the check for non-tty output streams. 
